{"tid":526315,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"住客交歡遭偷拍上網　酒店報警","createTime":"2018-01-11T13:39:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-12T12:57:25.000Z","uid":25558,"like":22,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"3dbc73a8c28cf126ef57f687073f970f450233e9","tid":526315,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T13:39:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180111/20270883\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180111%2F20270883&d=8e3Oxu1LYyWeB3VpSQnT4br9WXPazFMcT8p8rn878U0%3D&h=f60bc537\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180111%2F20270883&h=41df4abe\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180111/20270883</a><br />\n<br />\n住客交歡遭偷拍上網　酒店報警<br />\n<br />\n港聞   <br />\n         <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n0:00<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】港島天后一間酒店有住客私隱被偷拍！網上近日流傳兩段短片，分別拍得兩對男女及兩名女住客，在酒店房內春光乍洩，其中一對男女更在交歡，疑有人在附近大廈以長鏡頭拍得片段。<br />\n<br />\n涉事酒店位於威非路道，房間以落地玻璃窗設計。片段所見拍攝時間為日間，房內睡床貼近窗邊，當事人沒有落窗簾而被偷拍。其中一段偷拍影片長7分鐘，涉及兩間房的住客，其中一對男女正在交歡，更一度走至窗邊，赤裸貼着玻璃窗。同片其後鏡頭一轉，可見另一房間有兩名女住客，其中一人身體半裸露，兩人在床上用手機拍攝性感照片。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180111/large/11la6p30.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180111%2Flarge%2F11la6p30.jpg&h=7ca6976f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n涉事酒店房間裝有落地玻璃窗，從對面大廈可清楚看到房間內貌。互聯網<br />\n<br />\n私隱署關注事件<br />\n<br />\n片段近日在網上瘋傳，酒店於前晚報案，指有人疑未經同意下在上址拍攝住客，並將有關相片及影片上載互聯網。警方調查後，列有犯罪或不誠實意圖而取用電腦案，不排除有人從酒店對面的大廈單位，用長鏡頭向酒店房偷拍。<br />\n<br />\n個人資料私隱專員黃繼兒發聲明表示關注事件，強調不論使用任何裝置，包括相機、攝錄機等，特意在屬於私人空間收集他人私隱資料，並上載至互聯網或透過其他渠道披露，很大程度上可能觸犯《個人資料（私隱）條例》。<br />\n<br />\n■記者黎國剛"},{"pid":"77c1c6e88f2b498d6790dd8bb65ff58adc205f17","tid":526315,"uid":1065,"like":70,"dislike":2,"score":68,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T13:48:20.000Z","msg":"會唔會貼返啲單向玻璃貼會好啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"296435215793a228ab63a687be21a342ad70230e","tid":526315,"uid":119330,"like":19,"dislike":7,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"77c1c6e88f2b498d6790dd8bb65ff58adc205f17","tid":526315,"uid":1065,"like":70,"dislike":2,"score":68,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T13:48:20.000Z","msg":"會唔會貼返啲單向玻璃貼會好啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T13:50:07.000Z","msg":"附近D樓會唔會即刻升值<br />\n<br />\nBTW 遲下附近應該好多航拍機出沒"},{"pid":"879c7b43b5ff910d2339426b0cf5579116ea7d46","tid":526315,"uid":5929,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"quote":{"pid":"77c1c6e88f2b498d6790dd8bb65ff58adc205f17","tid":526315,"uid":1065,"like":70,"dislike":2,"score":68,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T13:48:20.000Z","msg":"會唔會貼返啲單向玻璃貼會好啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T14:00:05.000Z","msg":"夜晚房開左燈一樣睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3759a19b17c715cba7d65a1de3efac10ab1c395f","tid":526315,"uid":5499,"like":183,"dislike":0,"score":183,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T14:00:07.000Z","msg":"屌你自己d玻璃透哂都告人偷拍"},{"pid":"02176273c1774a3b1ff7a65a3b9d23b442c75d88","tid":526315,"uid":38548,"like":32,"dislike":8,"score":24,"quote":{"pid":"3759a19b17c715cba7d65a1de3efac10ab1c395f","tid":526315,"uid":5499,"like":183,"dislike":0,"score":183,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T14:00:07.000Z","msg":"屌你自己d玻璃透哂都告人偷拍"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T14:01:58.000Z","msg":"的確係犯法<br />\n舊登好似討論過 打開晒窗俾人影 影個個都係犯法<br />\n<br />\n有錯請指教"},{"pid":"c7ae8b20acd0e80fb50fa2541f538e738aab5781","tid":526315,"uid":5499,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"02176273c1774a3b1ff7a65a3b9d23b442c75d88","tid":526315,"uid":38548,"like":32,"dislike":8,"score":24,"quote":{"pid":"3759a19b17c715cba7d65a1de3efac10ab1c395f","tid":526315,"uid":5499,"like":183,"dislike":0,"score":183,"cite